Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.43,0:01:31.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}就会面对人间艰辛
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.52,0:01:36.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}在不论胜败之地我们相遇
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.48,0:01:40.49,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}描绘又擦去
